name: Gyoza-Salute! (饺敬Mix)
description:
!!! The exclamation mark is not optional !!!

！！！ 一定要加感叹号 ！！！

Gyoza-Salute! is a Bayesian block weight merge between GyozaMixV2 and SaluteMix. I would describe it as having the character and aesthetic sense of GyozaMix with the spacial, shading, and coloring sense of SaluteMix.

Laion gave it a aesthetic rating of 0.5367524297607529 (out of 10), which I think is pretty unfair given how good the ouputs are but Laion also would prefer that I stop making anime models (I refuse). Don't take Laion's word for it though. Look at the results, and I think it'll speak for itself.

Here's what it looks like visualized. The farther to the left it is, the more SaluteMix it has and the farther to the right it is the more GyozaMix it has.

As you can see the ratio is all over the place. Bayesian block weight merging is weird.
